sentences: Jeffrey James Logan (born May 7, 1978), better known by his stage name Jel, is an American hip hop producer and rapper.
Jel released his first solo album, 10 Seconds, on Mush Records in 2002.
His second solo album, Soft Money, was released on Anticon in 2006.
He released his third solo album, Late Pass, on Anticon in 2013.
In a 2006 interview with The Skinny, he said: "What inspires me lyrically is television conversations and dope MCs."
